text.section:
Each consumer member of the Board:
Shall be a member of the general public;
May not be or ever have been an occupational therapist or occupational therapy assistant or in training to become an occupational therapist or occupational therapy assistant;
May not have a household member who is an occupational therapist or occupational therapy assistant or in training to become an occupational therapist or occupational therapy assistant;
May not participate or ever have participated in a commercial or professional field related to occupational therapy;
May not have a household member who participates in a commercial or professional field related to occupational therapy; and
May not have had within 2 years before appointment a substantial financial interest in a person regulated by the Board.
